00:02:37.340 --> 00:02:40.710
That is, k is small, because
energy goes like k squared.

00:02:40.710 --> 00:02:43.410
If k is small, it's low energy.

00:02:43.410 --> 00:02:45.440
So these are the
possibilities that

00:02:45.440 --> 00:02:50.660
would allow us to
have a situation where

00:02:50.660 --> 00:02:53.270
only the first few
phase shifts contribute

00:02:53.270 --> 00:02:55.550
to the cross section.

00:02:55.550 --> 00:02:59.070
So let's see why
