00:05:18.220 --> 00:05:20.490
So what is our situation?

00:05:23.070 --> 00:05:27.780
In our situation, when we
consider a partial wave

00:05:27.780 --> 00:05:30.480
expansion, we're
considering waves

00:05:30.480 --> 00:05:35.220
