00:05:45.690 --> 00:05:48.930
where l is the quantum number.

00:05:51.730 --> 00:05:52.230
Number.

00:05:58.410 --> 00:06:01.200
The number that we're
fixing here each time

00:06:01.200 --> 00:06:07.230
