00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:54.990
It's a somewhat
classical intuition.

00:06:54.990 --> 00:06:57.300
But it gives you an idea.

00:06:57.300 --> 00:07:02.640
As you're increasing l, you're
increasing the impact parameter

00:07:02.640 --> 00:07:04.680
intuitively.

00:07:04.680 --> 00:07:09.900
A partial wave
scattering process with l

00:07:09.900 --> 00:07:12.600
