00:12:55.650 --> 00:12:57.875
k squared, over 2m.

00:13:03.030 --> 00:13:08.850
It's a solution of that
problem with that potential.

00:13:08.850 --> 00:13:12.530
So here is your intuition.

00:13:12.530 --> 00:13:18.680
This solution encounters
a barrier here.

00:13:18.680 --> 00:13:23.000
So it must be exponentially
suppressed in this distance.

00:13:23.000 --> 00:13:25.490
It will be
exponentially suppressed

00:13:25.490 --> 00:13:28.800
as you go below
this turning point.

00:13:28.800 --> 00:13:35.150
Therefore, this partial wave
will be 0 for some radius

00:13:35.150 --> 00:13:39.050
smaller to a certain
distance here.

00:13:39.050 --> 00:13:41.630
And that's back
of our intuition.

00:13:41.630 --> 00:13:45.590
If you have some impact
parameter this large,

00:13:45.590 --> 00:13:49.880
you have no support
