00:13:49.880 --> 00:13:51.710
than your impact parameter.

00:13:51.710 --> 00:13:52.910
There's no wave there.

00:13:52.910 --> 00:13:56.270
The wave stays away.

00:13:56.270 --> 00:14:01.580
So what we want to show is
