00:14:09.350 --> 00:14:12.520
to this thing.

00:14:12.520 --> 00:14:15.570
So what do we get?

00:14:15.570 --> 00:14:19.920
Well, we can solve
for the turning point.

00:14:19.920 --> 00:14:28.400
So h squared l, l plus 1
over 2mr star squared--

00:14:28.400 --> 00:14:31.760
I can call this r star--

00:14:31.760 --> 00:14:36.800
is equal to h squared,
k squared, over 2m.

00:14:36.800 --> 00:14:38.940
Lots of things cancel.

00:14:38.940 --> 00:14:40.690
2m's, h squared.

00:14:40.690 --> 00:14:50.030
So you get kr star
squared is roughly equal

00:14:50.030 --> 00:14:52.340
to l times l plus 1.

00:14:55.460 --> 00:14:59.530
And here, I can
approximate and I can

00:14:59.530 --> 00:15:06.470
