How much?

00:16:17.740 --> 00:16:19.540
The intuition is
that the distance

00:16:19.540 --> 00:16:21.730
approximate to the
input parameter,

00:16:21.730 --> 00:16:26.160
which is l divided by k.

00:16:26.160 --> 00:16:27.100
OK.

00:16:27.100 --> 00:16:30.800
So that's another
piece of intuition.

00:16:33.540 --> 00:16:37.110
There's one more
classical intuition

00:16:37.110 --> 00:16:41.960
