have that thing.

00:19:14.050 --> 00:19:17.070
It's a probability to
scatter in some direction,

00:19:17.070 --> 00:19:18.350
in some measure.

00:19:18.350 --> 00:19:21.580
So this is called
partial wave unitarity.

00:19:24.790 --> 00:19:27.415
Wave unitarity.

