in that partial wave.

00:26:03.860 --> 00:26:08.670
So it's going to
be 2 pi b delta b.

00:26:08.670 --> 00:26:15.350
And this is 2 pi l
over k times 1 over k.

00:26:15.350 --> 00:26:18.420
And that's not so bad.

00:26:18.420 --> 00:26:32.800
This is-- I'll write it as 1
